            "tag": "em",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Prerequisite: Dexterity 13 or higher"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "You are an expert at slinking through shadows. You gain the following benefits:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "You can try to hide when you are lightly obscured from the creature from which you are hiding."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "When you are hidden from a creature and miss it with a ranged weapon attack, making the attack doesn't reveal your position."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Dim light doesn't impose disadvantage on your Wisdom (Perception) checks relying on sight."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "html": "<div id=\"page-content\">\n<p>Source: Player's Handbook</p>\n<p><em>Prerequisite: Dexterity 13 or higher</em></p>\n<p>You are an expert at slinking through shadows. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You can try to hide when you are lightly obscured from the creature from which you are hiding.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>When you are hidden from a creature and miss it with a ranged weapon attack, making the attack doesn't reveal your position.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Dim light doesn't impose disadvantage on your Wisdom (Perception) checks relying on sight.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"
  }
